s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sumário","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O elemento&nbsp;<strong>HTML <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&lt;html&gt;</span>&nbsp;</strong>(ou <em>HTML root element</em>) representa a raiz de um HTML ou XHTML documento. Todos os outros elementos devem ser descendentes desse elemento.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Categorias de conteúdo</a></dfn> Nenhuma.</li>\n <li><dfn>Conteúdo permitido</dfn> Um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/head\"><code>&lt;head&gt;</code></a>, seguido por um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de tag</dfn>A tag inicial pode ser omitida se a primeira coisa dentro do elemento <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>&nbsp;não for um comentário.<br>\n  A tag final pode ser omitida se o elemento <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>&nbsp;não for imediatamente seguido por um comentário, e conter um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> ou &nbsp;que não está vazio, ou cuja tag inicial está presente.</li>\n <li><dfn>Elementos pais permitidos</dfn>Como o elemento raiz do documento, ou qualquer fragmento de subdocumento é permitido em um documento composto.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM interface</dfn> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLHtmlElement\"><code>HTMLhtmlElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Esse elemento inclui os </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"manifest\"><a id=\"attr-manifest\" href=\"#attr-manifest\"><b><code>manifest</code></b></a> <span class=\"badge inline html-version\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span> </dt>\n <dd>Especifica a URI de um recurso manifest indicando os recursos que devem ser carregados na memória local. Veja <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Using_the_application_cache\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Recursos offline em Firefox</a>&nbsp;para detalhes.</dd>\n <dt id=\"version\"><a id=\"attr-version\" href=\"#attr-version\"><b><code>version</code></b></a> <span class=\"notecard inline deprecated\" title=\"\">Deprecated since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML4.01</a></span> <span title=\"\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Obsolete since <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/HTML/HTML5\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">HTML5</a></span></dt>\n <dd>Especifica a versão da definição de tipo de documento HTML que governa o documento atual. Esse atributo não é necessário, porque é redundante com a informação de versão na declaração de tipo &nbsp;de documento.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O DOCTYPE usado no exemplo seguinte indica HTML5.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Desde que o elemento <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>&nbsp;seja o primeiro em documento outro que comenta, esse é chamado o elemento raiz. Embora essa tag possa ser implícita, ou não requerida, com&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML\" title=\"HTML\">HTML</a>, &nbsp;essa é requerida para ser aberta e fechada em&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XHTML\" title=\"XHTML\">XHTML</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-html-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;html&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/the-html-element.html#the-html-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;html&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/global.html#h-7.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;html&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade dos navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE&nbsp;Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Elemento de alto nível MathML: <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></li>\n <li>Elemento de alto nível SVG: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"sumário"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notas"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade dos navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <html> (ou HTML root element) representa a raiz de um HTML ou XHTML documento. Todos os outros elementos devem ser descendentes desse elemento.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<html>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<html>: The HTML Document / Root element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<html>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<html> : l'élément de racine du document HTML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<html>: HTML 文書 / ルート要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<html>: HTML 문서 / 루트 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<html>: Dokument HTML / Element Nadrzędny","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<html>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<html>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/html","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/html/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html","title":"<html>"}],"pageTitle":"<html> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}